\b ABOUT 
\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720
\cf0 Vivid is an annual Post-Rock/ Post-Metal festival held on the south coast in Norway. The first edition will be at the 25th and 26th of September 2015, aiming to establishing itself as a unique music festival emphasising audiovisual expressions, inclusion and hospitality. VIVID, \'93evocative, lifelike\cf2 \'94\cf0  describes not only our understanding of the post-rock genre - throughout the two days of the festival we want to expose post-rock to a new group of people, and to become a vivid cross road for both artists and audience, and musicians and visual artists. As part of the overall concept we will experiment with new ways of involving audience and audiovisual expressions. \
\pard\pardeftab720\ri380
\cf0 \
The festival is dependent on volunteer contributions from both artists, organisers and friends alike. Throughout the two day festival there will be tea- and food gatherings, and if we manage workshops where international artists playing at the festival shares some of their knowledge and experience. \
