\b TICKETS 
\b0 \
Tickets will be of three different types. \
1. Dagsbillett // Day ticket, for either 25th or 26th of September, 250 NKR\
2. Festivalpass // Festival ticket, for both 25th and 26th of September, 400 NKR\
3. Festivalpakke // Festival package, festival ticket including bed* and breakfast at the tiny festival hotel together with bands and fans, 1000 NKR (Juhu!)\
\
*beds are proper hotel beds, not dorm beds, but of logistic reasons you may have to share your room with others. \
\
You may purchase your ticket online or at the door (50 NKR extra). For online purchase, go to Hoopla (external link opening up in a new tab). The site is unfortunately only in norwegian, but here are the steps to follow for your ticket purchase in norwegian :) \
\
1. Go to Hoopla (external link opening up in a new tab)\
2. Select the ticket of your choice \
3. Select \'93Neste\'94, which means \'93Next\'94 in norwegian\
4. Choose between receiving your ticket by sms or email (probably preferable for non-norwegians).  \
